snippet: Sevilla reminded Barcelona and Real Madrid the title race is not a two-horse contest by producing a breathtaking first-half attacking show to crush local rivals Malaga 4-1 and go second in La Liga on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: Sevilla reminded Barcelona and Real Madrid the title race is not a two-horse contest by producing a breathtaking first-half attacking show to crush local rivals Malaga 4-1 and go second in La Liga on Saturday.

headline.main: Two-Horse Race? Think Again, Say Super Sevilla
headline.print_headline: Two-Horse Race? Think Again, Say Super Sevilla
